            "title": "",
            "text": "<p>We use UPS for all deliveries. </p><p>When your marinière is ready to be dispatched, we'll send you an email with your tracking details so you can follow your marinière's journey to you. </p><h2>Shipping times:</h2><p><strong>EU customers</strong> - 2 – 5 working days after dispatch.</p><p><strong>Rest of World customers</strong> - 3 - 7 working days after dispatch.</p><p>You'll get an email and/or text message from UPS with your tracking details. They will give an expected day of delivery and will attempt delivery up to 3 times. If your delivery failed and your marinière was returned to us, we would need to re-charge you for shipping a second attempt. </p><p></p><h2>Customs, Clearance & Duties Fees:</h2><p>We are unable to cover the cost of any customs, clearance or duties fees and so must be paid for by the customer.</p>",
